'''逸翁美术馆'''（{{jpn|j=逸翁美術館|hg=いつおうびじゅつかん|rm=Itsuō Bijyutsukan|f=y}}），是一个位于[[日本|日本]][[大阪府|大阪府]][[池田市|池田市]]的[[美术馆|美术馆]]。

==历史==
1957年建成开放，新馆1997年建成开放，是以企業家暨政治家[[小林一三|小林一三]]旧宅雅俗山庄改建而来，主要收藏小林一三的艺术藏品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.city.ikeda.osaka.jp/soshiki/siminseikatsu/kanko/gyomu/kanko/sinaikannkousisetsu/1415929739467.html |script-title=ja:逸翁美術館 |trans-title=Itsuo Art Museum |language=ja |publisher=[[Ikeda,_Osaka|Ikeda City]] |accessdate=31 October 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304073207/http://www.city.ikeda.osaka.jp/soshiki/siminseikatsu/kanko/gyomu/kanko/sinaikannkousisetsu/1415929739467.html |archive-date=4 March 2016 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hankyu-bunka.or.jp/about/itsuo-museum/index.html |script-title=ja:逸翁美術館 |trans-title=Itsuo Art Museum |language=ja |publisher=Itsuo Art Museum |accessdate=31 October 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151026200454/http://www.hankyu-bunka.or.jp/about/itsuo-museum/index.html |archivedate=26 October 2015 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hankyu-bunka.or.jp/about/collection/itsuo-museum/index.html |script-title=ja:逸翁美術館の収蔵品 |trans-title=Itsuo Art Museum - The Collection |language=ja |publisher=Itsuo Art Museum |accessdate=31 October 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151024093523/http://www.hankyu-bunka.or.jp/about/collection/itsuo-museum/index.html |archivedate=24 October 2015 }}</ref>。館名「逸翁」為他的[[號|雅號]]。

